<SP>
<SPEAKER>Dominus.</SPEAKER>
<L>God wot, y shal speke &thorn;e wyht,<NOTE PLACE="foot">God hit wot, I shal speken O; so God etc. E; wi&thorn; O, with E.</NOTE></L>
